01385\" alt=\"Hexagone middle\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" /></picture>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"wakeup-sec pos-relative\">\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-5 offset-md-5 col-6 offset-6\">\n                            <div class=\"wakeup-sec-inner\">\n                                <p>Let the Broadway Bright Detox Mask power you through those pulsating Manhattan nights while satisfying your soul (and skin) with a cathartic cleanse.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"true-water-cream\">\n                    <picture>\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-true-water-cream.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-true-water-cream-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-true-water-cream-mobile.png\" alt=\"true-water-cream\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" /></picture>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"purple-symbol\">\n                    <picture>\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-purple-symbol.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-purple-symbol-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-purple-symbol-mobile.png\" alt=\"Purple\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" /></picture>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"purple-symbol-text\">\n                    <p>Symbols in this collection</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"night-slider\">\n                <div class=\"container-fluid velvet-container-pdr-0\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-10 offset-md-2\">\n                            <div class=\"ovr-hid\">\n                                <div class=\"owl-carousel owl-theme the_velvet-slider\">\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Marigold</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider1.png\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider1-ipad.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider1-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider1-mobile.png\" alt=\"Marigold\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" /></picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Marigold</h2>\n                                                <p>Our body is a temple, making interactions with the skin nothing short of rituals. Intrinsically Indian and supremely sacred at the same time, these saffron symbols of tradition are not only essential in garlands and ceremonies, but also effective in their power to soothe the skin and reduce blemishes.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Palash</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider2.png\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider2-ipad.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider2-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider2-mobile.png\" alt=\"Palash\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" /></picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Palash</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider2-p\">Also recognized as the flame of the forest, Palash purifies and transforms skin. Rich in sulfur, this flaming red symbol of spring is traditionally only offered to Lord Agni, the God of Fire, but is now also a sacred part of your detoxifying ritual.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Assamese Script</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider3.png\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider3-ipad.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider3-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider3-mobile.png\" alt=\"Assamese Script\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" /></picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Assamese Script</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider3-p\">In its journey from medieval to modern, the Assamese Script has evolved time and time again. The script is defined by its simplicity and symmetry, the gentle curves of the letters mimicking the slopes that have come to define the region.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Broadway Lights</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider4.png?v=1606201698\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider4-ipad.png?v=1606201697\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider4-mobile.png?v=1606201698\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-velvet-slider4-mobile.png?v=1606201698\" alt=\"Broadway Lights\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" /></picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Broadway Lights</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider4-p\">A promise of romance, glamour and drama, the heart and pulse of New York lies on Broadway - the sky dotted with marquee lights, bright signs at every corner, and rolled out red carpets waiting for the stars to step out into the spotlight. Where the lights are always on and the show must always go on. On Broadway, it’s always your moment to shine.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div clas